OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FAny evening
OL,6,Fbrightness will be short-lived as
OL,7,Fcloud quickly thickens from the west.
OL,8,FMostly dry before midnight but turning
OL,9,Fbreezy. Heavier and more persistent
OL,10,Frain spreads northeast after midnight,
OL,11,Fclearing soon after dawn. Mild.
OL,12,
OL,13,CWednesday:FCloudy start, perhaps some
OL,14,Fearly rain in the east. Most parts
OL,15,Fbecoming dry and rather warm, before
OL,16,Flocally heavy rain and gusty winds
OL,17,Fmove east from late afternoon.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
