OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:FSunny
OL,6,Fspells and showers Thursday. Cloudier
OL,7,FFriday, but mostly dry, before a
OL,8,Fweakening band of rain spreads east
OL,9,Flater. Sunny spells and showers
OL,10,FSaturday. Warm in any brighter spells.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
